description: Simply say a phrase such as "give me a dog fact" or "tell me a fact" and this skill set will fulfill all your dog trivia wonders and needs.
exampleInteractions: Alexa, ask doggo trivia to give me a dog fact
Alexa, ask doggo trivia to tell me something
Alexa, ask doggo trivia to give me some information
name: My Dog Facts
shortDescription: Ever find yourself itching to learn some random facts about dogs? Ever wonder how amazing dogs can be? Looking to pass time? This is the skill set for you!
